long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rediscover Your Browsing Journey with LivingHistory.

By clicking “Add to Chrome”, you accept and agree to install the LivingHistory extension, set the Chrome™ default search to LivingHistory, and to the Terms of Use, and Privacy Policy.

Terms of Use: https://www.live-history.com/terms-of-use 
Privacy Policy: https://www.live-history.com/privacy-policy

Not just a search engine, LivingHistory is your browsing companion to search, save and access to the last 10 searches. 
Search for "livinghistory" in the address bar and rediscover the way you browse!
